    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Oath of Vengeance</strong></p><p>When you see a creature harm an ally or a helpless creature within 30 feet of you, you may mark that creature as your <strong>Sworn Foe</strong> (no action required).</p><p><strong>Until the end of your next turn, while raging:</strong></p><ul><li>You gain a +1 bonus to attack rolls against your Sworn Foe.</li><li>The first time you hit your Sworn Foe, the target takes additional damage equal to your proficiency bonus.</li></ul><p>You can have only one Sworn Foe at a time.</p><hr /><p><strong>Auspice Interaction (Choose One)</strong></p><p>Your Auspice grants an additional rider when you swear your vengeance. This rider is determined by your Auspice.</p>",
